{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>轻骁吧是一个阉割版的骁吧。<br>做轻骁吧的目的是参加编程比赛。<br>所以做好了也会考虑开源。<br></p>","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2017-05-23 15:01:05","replyCount":0,"signKey":"my/welcome.jpg","source":"","sourceUrl":"","tid":2690},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>轻骁吧需要脱离骁之屋网站的环境而存在，所以不能借用网站的导航栏、用户系统和消息系统。<br>但是导航栏、用户系统和消息系统又是这样一个论坛的基本存在。<br>所以轻骁吧要自带简易的导航栏、用户系统、消息系统。<br></p>","floor":2,"pid":5429,"postTime":"2017-05-23 15:05:05","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2690},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>轻骁吧也要跟七牛云对接，但不和骁之屋主站共享同一个七牛云空间。<br>当然轻骁吧的数据也不是和主站共享的。<br></p>","floor":3,"pid":5430,"postTime":"2017-05-23 15:07:18","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2690},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"先考虑导航栏和用户系统。<br><br>导航栏只需要显示“轻骁吧”的logo和当前用户。<br>用户系统只做三部分：注册、登录、修改头像。其余一律不做。<br>注册的时候只需要填写用户名和密码就可以了。<br>","floor":4,"pid":5431,"postTime":"2017-05-23 15:14:30","replyCount":2,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2690,"initComments":{"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"增加一个必填项，性别","createTime":"2017-05-23 15:33:57","id":2167,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"在用户登录状态下 允许修改头像、性别、编辑个人简介。不然个人主页没什么好写的。","createTime":"2017-05-23 15:34:28","id":2168,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/F